Used in Fission Reactors. Use Fuel Ports to Load/Unload.

Irradiates items with neutron flux. 
Has to be placed in one line with moderator and fuel cell behind it.

nc.guide_book.desc: Basics and advanced topics about NuclearCraft
nc.guide_book.name: NuclearCraft Guide
processor.description.analyzer: Used to analyze environment and items.
processor.description.decay_hastener: Accelerates decay speed of radioactive materials.
processor.description.electrolyzer: Separates fluids and gases into their components.
processor.description.fluid_enricher: Enriches fluids and gases with solid items.
processor.description.fluid_infuser: Mixes fluids with items to get new items.
processor.description.ingot_former: Forms solid items from molten liquids.
processor.description.irradiator: Transform items and fluids with the power of Radiative Flux. Needs to be placed in reactor's wall.
processor.description.leacher: Leaches undeground minerals with acids and pumps slurry back.
processor.description.manufactory: Crushes items into dusts and other materials.
processor.description.nuclear_furnace: Very fast furnace which uses uranium ingots as fuel.
processor.description.pump: Pumps fluids and gasses from environment.
processor.description.steam_turbine: Produce energy with power of steam.
processor_side_config.title: Select Slot
processor_slot_mode.title: Slot Mode
tooltip.nc.bearing.desc: Connects the rotor shaft to the turbine wall and dynamo. Must cover the full area of each end of the shaft.
tooltip.nc.blade.desc: Converts the energy of the oncoming fluid flow into rotational energy in the rotor shaft. The expansion coefficient is larger than unity, so the volume of the fluid flow will increase each time it passes through a set. Must be placed in complete sets of four coplanar groups extending from the turbine shaft to the wall. Each blade block can process up to %s of oncoming fluid.
tooltip.nc.fusion_casing.descr: Used to build toroidal fusion reactor chamber
tooltip.nc.fusion_connector.descr: Used to connect fusion core and toroidal reactor chamber
tooltip.nc.hev.desc: Grants additional protection and passive effects when charged
tooltip.nc.jei.gas_to_fluid.desc: NC blocks automatically converts Mek Gasses into Fluids during input
tooltip.nc.moderator.desc:
Fission Reactor moderator. Has to be placed next to fuel cell. 
 Each adjacent with fuel cell adds +%s%% efficiency and +%s%% heat gen
tooltip.nc.multitool.desc: Commonly used to config sides of batteries, barrels, ports...
tooltip.nc.multitool.shift.desc: Sneak + RBM to config back side
tooltip.nc.rotor_shaft.desc: Connects the rotor blades to the dynamo to convert the generated kinetic energy into electrical energy. Must be placed axially as a cuboid along the centre of the turbine interior.
tooltip.nc.shielding.desc: Combine with armor in crafting grid
tooltip.nc.use_in_leacher: Item can be used in Leacher
